abstract: ALBANY, Oct. 7.--Gov. Hill is reported to be getting nervous. Already, at the threshold of his campaign, his courage begins to fail. abstract: LEETONIA, Ohio, Oct. 13.--Early this morning, while a number of employes were standing within a few feet of the newly built furnace of the Cherry Valley Company, several tons of hot metal, coke, and limestone suddenly burst upon them. The men were all married, and each had a large family.
